{"tid":1896063,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"孔聖堂的春袋？","createTime":"2020-02-25T02:06:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T09:49:17.000Z","uid":212405,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"85f47b8c003a20f5817bcc5f3205fced89a4343a","tid":1896063,"uid":212405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T02:06:20.000Z","msg":"老實講大家係孔聖堂中學個FB罵，有鬼用。<br />\n孔聖堂中學只係間本來差唔多要殺校，轉直資先保得住間學校。 <br />\n明顯孔聖堂中學不嬲就係孔聖堂既負資產。 <br />\n<br />\n咁郁到啲咩孔聖堂先會肉痛，<br />\n我上網見到一間叫做「晉德學校」（Chinese Academy）的私立小學（佢係度扮自己係國際學校）<br />\n學費全年 13萬。 <br />\n睇個介紹，似係target 真係信中國儒教 啲鬼佬 。 <br />\n姐係好似外國人仰慕儒教，但去左孔子學院讀咁膠....<br />\n私立學校啲學校真係可以袋落袋架...<br />\n<br />\n FB ： <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chineseacademyhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fchineseacademyhk%2F&d=2snho0MtSZbn8sjHWbtmpcorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=198f7e33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/chineseacademyhk/</a><br />\n學校網址： <a href=\"https://caps.edu.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcaps.edu.hk%2F&d=2snho0MtSZbn8sjHWbtmpcorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=ceca9452\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://caps.edu.hk/</a>"},{"pid":"72dc560f13850c7d5f46e9b5d9a24712bf770f15","tid":1896063,"uid":212405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T02:08:02.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n推推"},{"pid":"e81854310dcd309318d59409efc87d348bb5b4f6","tid":1896063,"uid":258010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T02:08:08.000Z","msg":"P can&rsquo;t pish"},{"pid":"09d3745add3e0487f76c1fe61b88045492f32e02","tid":1896063,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T02:11:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fd4c85f4a6d8c1b5eeb12812e7e46b35f0a0dd97","tid":1896063,"uid":102331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T02:12:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal